\begin_layout Section
Requirements
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In order to satisfy goals in section [Section Goals] under domain assumptions
 in Section [Section domain Assumption] we've derived requirements for our
 system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[G1.1] USER should be able to reserve a car:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
[R1] The system can modify car's status (available, occupied, in use).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[R2] The system shall be able to know car's status.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[R2] The system shall reserve a car only if the car is available.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[R3] The system shall be able to associate a car to the USER who has reserved
 it.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
[G1.2] USER should be able to unlock reseved car when they are close to it.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
[R4] The system shall know cars' location according to cars' GPS.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[R5] The system shall know user's location according to his GPS.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[R6] The system shall provide a functionality to unlock the car.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[D1]
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[D2]
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[D3]
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
[G1.3] USER should be aware of how much they are going to pay during the
 ride.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
[R7] The system shall be able to calculate ride's cost based on duration.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[R8] The system shall be able to communicate to the car ride's cost.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
[D4]
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
[G2] The reservation of two (or more) cars at a time must be forbidden.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
[R7] The system shall reserve a car only if the user hasn't already reserved
 another car.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
